107
00:07:12,710 --> 00:07:14,410
Kim Jiwan!

108
00:07:24,250 --> 00:07:25,580
What are you doing here?

109
00:07:25,580 --> 00:07:27,880
Well, I...

110
00:07:28,450 --> 00:07:31,080
I was passing by, and...

111
00:07:31,080 --> 00:07:32,910
I was walking by, and...

112
00:07:34,780 --> 00:07:37,140
