140
00:09:49,010 --> 00:09:51,710
Oh, I see.

141
00:09:51,710 --> 00:09:54,140
When are you going home?

142
00:09:54,150 --> 00:09:55,840
I'm on my way.

143
00:09:55,850 --> 00:09:58,140
I hear the shaved ice at

144
00:09:58,150 --> 00:10:00,040
the cafe you frequent is good.

145
00:10:00,050 --> 00:10:03,650
Yes, their coffee and shaved ice are all good.

146
00:10:03,650 --> 00:10:05,110
I should go there, then.

147
00:10:05,110 --> 00:10:06,380
Okay.

148
00:10:11,050 --> 00:10:13,410
Honey, what should we have for dinner?

149
00:10:13,410 --> 00:10:14,840
Spring vegetables are in season.

150
00:10:14,850 --> 00:10:16,480
Should I make some dishes?

151
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:17,780
It's okay.

152
00:10:17,780 --> 00:10:19,450
Let's just eat whatever we have.

153
00:10:20,510 --> 00:10:22,350
It's dinner time. Where are you going?

154
00:10:22,350 --> 00:10:23,350
Mom, I'll be right back.

155
00:10:23,350 --> 00:10:24,910
Have dinner without me.

156
00:10:26,880 --> 00:10:29,980
Honey, did you see her?

157
00:10:29,980 --> 00:10:30,880
I did.

158
00:10:30,880 --> 00:10:32,880
Why did she get all dressed up?

159
00:10:32,880 --> 00:10:34,610
I'm suspicious of her.

160
00:10:34,610 --> 00:10:36,180
Maybe she went out to meet a man.

161
00:11:03,350 --> 00:11:04,550
Jiwan.

162
00:11:05,410 --> 00:11:06,380
When did you get here?

163
00:11:06,380 --> 00:11:07,810
Hi, Yeongju.

164
00:11:07,810 --> 00:11:10,110
Were you at a wedding?

165
00:11:10,110 --> 00:11:11,140
What?

166
00:11:11,980 --> 00:11:13,550
I was on my way home...

167
00:11:15,310 --> 00:11:18,710
You're having shaved ice and coffee alone?

168
00:11:18,710 --> 00:11:19,940
What?

169
00:11:19,950 --> 00:11:21,450
I'm not alone.

170
00:11:21,450 --> 00:11:22,310
What?

171
00:11:39,050 --> 00:11:40,880
We're having a launching show

172
00:11:40,880 --> 00:11:42,680
at the Da Vinci Hotel near here.

173
00:11:42,680 --> 00:11:43,980
We've been there to check it out.

174
00:11:44,810 --> 00:11:45,880
I see.

175
00:11:46,380 --> 00:11:47,550
You want to join us?

176
00:11:48,150 --> 00:11:51,940
No, I came in because I saw you.

177
00:11:51,950 --> 00:11:53,040
I should go.

178
00:12:21,750 --> 00:12:23,980
Okay...

179
00:12:23,980 --> 00:12:27,310
Co-workers can have shaved ice together.

180
00:12:27,310 --> 00:12:29,140
It was a hot day today.

181
00:12:33,710 --> 00:12:37,680
