182
00:12:47,650 --> 00:12:49,510
Those cookies.

183
00:12:51,710 --> 00:12:52,450
Yes?

184
00:12:52,450 --> 00:12:54,080
Don't ever make them again.

185
00:12:55,650 --> 00:12:56,710
What?

186
00:12:56,710 --> 00:12:58,650
What kind of cookies were they?

187
00:12:58,650 --> 00:13:01,240
They were all broken, sweet and bitter.

188
00:13:01,250 --> 00:13:03,080
How could you be so bad at it?

189
00:13:04,050 --> 00:13:05,680
Don't ever make them again.

190
00:13:05,680 --> 00:13:07,280
You can't bake.

191
00:13:08,010 --> 00:13:10,210
Fine. I'll never make them again.

192
00:13:10,210 --> 00:13:12,110
And don't ever get hurt again.

193
00:13:19,710 --> 00:13:21,880
You've worn this all day, right?

194
00:13:21,880 --> 00:13:23,450
It's time to change it.

195
00:13:38,750 --> 00:13:40,350
What's wrong with you?

196
00:13:40,350 --> 00:13:43,980
