197
00:13:43,980 --> 00:13:46,040
Stop getting hurt.

198
00:13:46,650 --> 00:13:48,280
It bothers me.

199
00:13:49,580 --> 00:13:51,280
Don't let it bother you.

200
00:13:51,280 --> 00:13:53,580
Then make sure I won't be bothered.

201
00:13:55,680 --> 00:13:57,410
You should be more careful.

202
00:14:12,310 --> 00:14:15,410
I like shaved ice, too.

203
00:14:37,550 --> 00:14:38,410
Yeongju.

204
00:14:38,410 --> 00:14:40,040
Open this door.

205
00:14:40,050 --> 00:14:41,680
Why was your mascara running?

206
00:14:41,680 --> 00:14:42,810
Were you crying?

207
00:14:42,810 --> 00:14:44,040
Leave her alone.

208
00:14:44,050 --> 00:14:46,210
She wants to be alone.

209
00:14:46,210 --> 00:14:47,650
Did she grow up alone?

210
00:14:47,650 --> 00:14:49,350
I raised her when she was growing up,

211
00:14:49,350 --> 00:14:50,880
so why does she want to be left alone now?

212
00:14:50,880 --> 00:14:52,880
Yeongju!

213
00:14:52,880 --> 00:14:55,210
Open this door! Tell me what it is!

214
00:14:55,210 --> 00:14:56,110
Why are you crying?

215
00:14:56,110 --> 00:14:59,110
You want me to die of frustration?

216
00:15:05,880 --> 00:15:08,180
What's going on?

217
00:15:08,180 --> 00:15:09,980
What is it? Tell me so we can resolve it.

218
00:15:09,980 --> 00:15:11,550
What is it?

219
00:15:13,210 --> 00:15:14,380
My foot...

220
00:15:14,380 --> 00:15:15,650
What?

221
00:15:15,650 --> 00:15:17,480
What's wrong with your foot?

222
00:15:18,880 --> 00:15:21,080
I got a blister.

223
00:15:22,250 --> 00:15:25,680
What? Your foot looks fine.

224
00:15:26,550 --> 00:15:29,080
Oh, that looks like it hurts.

225
00:15:29,080 --> 00:15:31,240
Does that happen when you wear heels?

226
00:15:34,010 --> 00:15:36,610
Why didn't you wear your normal shoes?

227
00:15:36,610 --> 00:15:38,040
I knew you were making a mistake.

228
00:15:38,050 --> 00:15:41,080
Why did you do that? Just be yourself.

229
00:15:42,010 --> 00:15:43,210
Right.

230
00:15:44,110 --> 00:15:46,580
I should just be myself...

231
00:16:05,810 --> 00:16:06,940
What are you talking about?

232
00:16:06,950 --> 00:16:10,210
Eunsu framed someone of plagiarism to win?

233
00:16:10,210 --> 00:16:12,650
I don't know why people are saying that.

234
00:16:13,210 --> 00:16:15,980
I think it started at Design.

235
00:16:15,980 --> 00:16:17,880
I've been ignoring it because it's false,

236
00:16:17,880 --> 00:16:19,450
but it's gotten out of control.

237
00:16:19,450 --> 00:16:20,910
Out of control? How?

238
00:16:20,910 --> 00:16:23,940
They're saying Hyeondo's got her back.

239
00:16:23,950 --> 00:16:25,380
That's nonsense.

240
00:16:26,110 --> 00:16:27,880
Hyeondo's the one who

241
00:16:27,880 --> 00:16:29,550
discovered the plagiarism,

242
00:16:29,550 --> 00:16:31,580
