243
00:16:31,580 --> 00:16:33,650
People in Design spread that rumor?

244
00:16:42,010 --> 00:16:43,280
Would you like this?

245
00:16:43,910 --> 00:16:45,280
It's okay.

246
00:16:46,080 --> 00:16:49,710
You never say yes to anything I give you.

247
00:17:19,610 --> 00:17:20,810
That girl over there.

248
00:17:20,810 --> 00:17:22,210
They framed the winner for

249
00:17:22,210 --> 00:17:23,580
plagiarism to make her win.

250
00:17:24,980 --> 00:17:27,980
She must know some powerful people.

251
00:17:27,980 --> 00:17:30,450
She's got no experience or a degree.

252
00:17:31,010 --> 00:17:33,040
Everyone thought it was weird.

253
00:17:37,210 --> 00:17:38,280
Really?

254
00:17:39,110 --> 00:17:40,480
Everyone in Design is waiting

255
00:17:40,480 --> 00:17:41,810
for the right moment to get her.

256
00:17:53,080 --> 00:17:54,650
I'm sorry.

257
00:17:54,650 --> 00:17:55,580
Are you all right?

258
00:17:55,580 --> 00:17:56,940
Yes, I'm all right.

259
00:17:56,950 --> 00:17:58,210
I'm sorry.

260
00:17:59,250 --> 00:18:01,240
Oh, no.

261
00:18:16,710 --> 00:18:18,780
Everyone's watching, so just go.

262
00:18:22,910 --> 00:18:24,650
Hyeondo.

263
00:18:24,650 --> 00:18:26,380
Who cares if anyone's watching?

264
00:18:26,380 --> 00:18:27,710
Did you commit a crime?

265
00:18:27,710 --> 00:18:30,610
Why do you care about what others think?

266
00:18:34,250 --> 00:18:35,480
Thank you.

267
00:18:46,250 --> 00:18:48,710
Didn't I tell you to lower

268
00:18:48,710 --> 00:18:50,350
