281
00:19:23,110 --> 00:19:25,650
Must I point out every single detail?

282
00:19:25,650 --> 00:19:28,110
Aren't you ashamed of getting paid?

283
00:19:28,110 --> 00:19:29,480
Kim Jiwan!

284
00:19:29,480 --> 00:19:30,550
Come with me.

285
00:19:32,110 --> 00:19:33,380
Let go!

