00:51:54,810 --> 00:51:58,980
I heard you're Eunsu's birth mother.

844
00:51:59,650 --> 00:52:03,780
Seonhui told you I'm her birth mother?

845
00:52:03,780 --> 00:52:05,740
That's unexpected.

846
00:52:05,750 --> 00:52:09,040
You're acting like you're Seonhui's real son.

847
00:52:10,910 --> 00:52:13,080
Does Eunsu work here?

848
00:52:13,080 --> 00:52:14,780
At the hotel?

849
00:52:17,480 --> 00:52:18,940
Once was enough,

850
00:52:18,950 --> 00:52:21,010
so why would I come see her again?

851
00:52:21,510 --> 00:52:23,210
That girl...

852
00:52:23,210 --> 00:52:24,680
She grew up to be a pretty young lady.

853
00:52:26,010 --> 00:52:28,240
She must have a lot of admirers.

854
00:52:28,250 --> 00:52:32,710
So you didn't come here for Eunsu?

855
00:52:33,710 --> 00:52:35,350
Mother and I thought...

856
00:52:36,550 --> 00:52:37,880
I haven't seen her for over 20 years,

857
00:52:37,880 --> 00:52:39,780
so why would I start now?

858
00:52:39,780 --> 00:52:41,840
Seonhui's so weird.

859
00:52:41,850 --> 00:52:44,610
She think's everyone in the world is like her.

860
00:52:45,280 --> 00:52:47,110
If that's the reason, I want to leave.

861
00:52:47,950 --> 00:52:51,680
Why did you give Eunsu away?

862
00:52:53,510 --> 00:52:56,210
Even if things were bad,

863
00:52:56,210 --> 00:52:58,610
you could've come to see her.

864
00:53:00,050 --> 00:53:02,080
Didn't Seonhui tell you?

865
00:53:02,950 --> 00:53:08,580
I didn't leave Eunsu with Seonhui.

866
00:53:11,210 --> 00:53:12,650
I abandoned her.

867
00:53:15,150 --> 00:53:18,310
You're making me feel like an evil witch.

868
00:53:18,310 --> 00:53:21,450
To be honest, Seonhui was a better choice.

869
00:53:21,450 --> 00:53:24,940
I had no idea Sangjun would go bankrupt.

870
00:53:25,450 --> 00:53:27,450
I thought about pros and cons

871
00:53:27,450 --> 00:53:29,550
and abandoned Eunsu for her sake.

872
00:53:29,550 --> 00:53:32,080
How could you say such a thing...

873
00:53:33,150 --> 00:53:35,680
Seonhui raised you into a stuffy man.

874
00:53:35,680 --> 00:53:38,010
Is Eunsu as stuffy as you are?

875
00:53:57,110 --> 00:53:58,380
Jiwan!

876
00:53:59,250 --> 00:54:00,350
They are looking for you inside.

877
00:54:00,350 --> 00:54:01,650
Hurry up and go.

878
00:54:02,010 --> 00:54:04,810
Are you crazy? How could you leave?

879
00:54:06,310 --> 00:54:07,450
- Eunsu. 
 - Seriously,

880
00:54:07,450 --> 00:54:09,040
whenever you create this kind of trouble,

881
00:54:09,050 --> 00:54:10,740
I don't know how to handle it.

882
00:54:14,080 --> 00:54:15,210
Right.

883
00:54:15,210 --> 00:54:17,180
I'm sorry for being an irresponsible brother.

884
00:54:17,650 --> 00:54:20,310
But you love having mom and me, right?

885
00:54:21,350 --> 00:54:23,710
What? What are you talking about?

886
00:54:23,710 --> 00:54:24,980
Hurry up and come.

887
00:54:46,380 --> 00:54:49,010
Gather around, everyone in Marketing!

888
00:54:49,010 --> 00:54:51,550
You've done a great job today.

889
00:54:51,550 --> 00:54:53,510
Thanks to all your hard work,

890
00:54:53,510 --> 00:54:56,310
the launching show went well.

891
00:54:56,310 --> 00:54:58,650
Let's enjoy today, okay?

892
00:54:59,580 --> 00:55:04,350
I'm taking you all out for a drink!

893
00:55:09,450 --> 00:55:11,110
Let's go.

894
00:55:14,350 --> 00:55:15,380
Just like I said,

895
00:55:15,380 --> 00:55:17,980
what do you think I did at that moment?

896
00:55:17,980 --> 00:55:20,310
As the team leader, I couldn't sit and watch.

897
00:55:20,310 --> 00:55:21,610
I stepped forward.

898
00:55:23,350 --> 00:55:25,380
I hate stepping forward, but I did.

899
00:55:25,380 --> 00:55:28,350
Why? Because I had no choice. Okay?

900
00:55:28,780 --> 00:55:30,410
You're amazing, Mr. Yun.

901
00:55:31,950 --> 00:55:33,180
By the way, Eunsu.

902
00:55:33,180 --> 00:55:33,980
Yes?

903
00:55:33,980 --> 00:55:34,710
What are you looking at

904
00:55:34,710 --> 00:55:36,040
when I'm talking to you?

905
00:55:36,680 --> 00:55:37,910
No, sir.

906
00:55:37,910 --> 00:55:39,280
I'm paying attention to you.

907
00:55:39,280 --> 00:55:41,510
See?

908
00:55:41,510 --> 00:55:44,910
This is why I like you so much.

909
00:55:44,910 --> 00:55:46,510
You're affable.

910
00:55:46,510 --> 00:55:48,280
Of your friends...

911
00:55:51,950 --> 00:55:53,410
Where did Jiwan go?

912
00:55:53,410 --> 00:55:54,880
He had to finish something up

913
00:55:54,880 --> 00:55:56,140
at the launching show.

914
00:55:56,150 --> 00:55:59,310
- I couldn't handle it. 
 - He should've told me.

915
00:55:59,780 --> 00:56:02,010
Jiwan is such a responsible person, right?

916
00:56:02,010 --> 00:56:03,350
Jiwan is.

917
00:56:04,250 --> 00:56:05,280
So...

918
00:56:05,280 --> 00:56:06,740
Where was I?

919
00:56:07,380 --> 00:56:08,810
I didn't know which parking lot it was.

920
00:56:08,810 --> 00:56:11,350
So what could I do to get out of this trouble?

921
00:56:11,350 --> 00:56:12,910
What kind of strategy...

922
00:56:18,850 --> 00:56:23,080
Mr. Jang Hyeondo

923
00:56:24,110 --> 00:56:28,080
Still, how could he leave without a word?

924
00:56:31,480 --> 00:56:33,410
Is he mad because I told him

925
00:56:33,410 --> 00:56:35,240
not to be friendly at work?

926
00:56:38,410 --> 00:56:40,680
He can be so petty.

927
00:57:08,580 --> 00:57:09,780
Mr. Jang Hyeondo

928
00:57:20,050 --> 00:57:22,380
Why did you leave early?

929
00:57:22,380 --> 00:57:25,110
You told me never to be friendly at work.

930
00:57:25,850 --> 00:57:28,310
Still, you didn't even look at me...

931
00:57:29,250 --> 00:57:31,310
It feels better not to look at you.

932
00:57:33,710 --> 00:57:35,380
Don't you miss me?

933
00:57:36,310 --> 00:57:38,480
But I see you every day.

934
00:57:38,480 --> 00:57:42,510
Not by passing, with other people.

935
00:57:42,510 --> 00:57:43,840
Not like that.

936
00:57:44,310 --> 00:57:46,350
Even just in passing,

937
00:57:46,350 --> 00:57:49,010
it's nice to see you regardless.

938
00:57:50,980 --> 00:57:52,510
I don't like it.

939
00:57:55,550 --> 00:57:58,550
My mom thinks you'll only last a month.

940
00:57:58,550 --> 00:58:00,780
Your family thinks I'm just Jiwan's friend.

941
00:58:00,780 --> 00:58:03,410
Jiwan has put off his decision on me.

942
00:58:03,410 --> 00:58:07,110
And I can't be friendly with you at work.

943
00:58:08,010 --> 00:58:10,010
Why does it have to be this complicated?

944
00:58:11,280 --> 00:58:13,380
My love life has never been this complicated.

945
00:58:13,380 --> 00:58:16,280
If I like someone, great. If not, it ends.

946
00:58:16,910 --> 00:58:18,650
It used to be so simple.

947
00:58:19,450 --> 00:58:21,880
So why is this so complicated?

948
00:58:23,210 --> 00:58:26,650
So you're unhappy?

949
00:58:26,650 --> 00:58:28,650
Yes.

950
00:58:28,650 --> 00:58:30,350
I'm unhappy.

951
00:58:31,950 --> 00:58:35,980
You want to end this?

952
00:58:47,580 --> 00:58:49,210
I do.

953
00:58:50,580 --> 00:58:55,510
I thought I could end it if I wanted to,

954
00:58:57,610 --> 00:58:59,510
but just thinking about it terrifies me.

955
00:59:01,680 --> 00:59:04,350
Not being able to take you to places,

956
00:59:04,350 --> 00:59:07,080
not being able to do anything for you.

957
00:59:07,680 --> 00:59:09,580
I hate all that.

958
00:59:12,550 --> 00:59:14,810
But...

959
00:59:14,810 --> 00:59:19,040
But even if things get complicated,

960
00:59:20,010 --> 00:59:24,380
let's see how far we can go.

961
00:59:47,210 --> 00:59:50,280
Your call is being forwarded to an automated...

962
00:59:52,350 --> 00:59:54,940
Eunsu, why aren't you picking up?

963
00:59:55,410 --> 00:59:57,040
Call me as soon as you hear this...

